&lt;li&gt;Collect, review, validate, and prepare payroll inputs, including employee changes, compensation updates, benefits deductions, and other payroll-related transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain payroll records and ensure all employee data changes are accurately documented and processed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with local payroll providers (including Briddge, Black Mountain, and other vendors) to ensure accurate and timely payroll execution.&lt;/li&gt;
