&lt;li&gt;Validate statutory and voluntary deductions to ensure compliance with local payroll and tax regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate and resolve payroll issues, discrepancies, and employee inquiries in a timely and professional manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a primary point of contact for employee payroll-related questions across EMEA and APAC.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with HR, Finance, Benefits, and external vendors to ensure payroll processes are aligned and operating effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain payroll documentation and support internal and external audit requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities for process improvements and participate in payroll-related projects and system enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure payroll activities comply with company policies, local regulations, and data privacy requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
