&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of payroll, HR operations, finance, or related experience, preferably within a multinational environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to international payroll processing is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
