&lt;p&gt;The Senior Product Associate will also act as a representative of the scrum team when engaging with internal and external stakeholders, ensuring alignment and incorporating feedback into the product roadmap. This role plays a key part in driving change, championing new ideas, and aligning and motivating teams to deliver against shared objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Help Take Us There&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
