&lt;li&gt;Prioritize the backlog of work so that it best supports the execution of the product strategy - write, refine, and prioritize user stories with clear acceptance criteria.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Product Managers to ensure the delivery of coherent and consistently high-quality products delivered at pace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineering, UX, and business teams to ensure alignment on feature development and technical feasibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with developers and QA to clarify requirements, troubleshoot issues, and validate feature completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze user and market data for insight on what is driving client behavior. Use this data to produce insightful sales material that will drive product usage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and track key product performance metrics, using data to drive continuous improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be comfortable show casing progress to large groups through demos and walkthroughs on topics such as client case studies, user feedback summaries, or product previews to demonstrate value and progress.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the head of product management in tracking business key performance indicators to measure product ROI/success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend meetings with investor clients or dealers and provide product expertise.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
