&lt;li&gt;Conduct regular client engagement through calls, meetings, and onsite visits; assess engagement effectiveness and adjust coverage accordingly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel regionally and internationally as required to visit clients, attend conferences, and engage with MarketAxess offices.&lt;/li&gt;
